{"tid":1515233,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(亂世中不忘湊細細路)點樣用木玩具教顏色？","createTime":"2019-08-29T05:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:08:10.000Z","uid":297465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f905674e5ebf5df3aa13456cfa045da419eacc8","tid":1515233,"uid":297465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"雖然依家正值關鍵時刻，不過相信好多巴絲都有好細個既細佬細妹，都要湊住佢地，但唔知點教佢地好...<br />\n<br />\n小弟返教會，有時見到d小朋友都好頭痛，聽聞五顏六色既木玩具可以幫細路仔認顏色，特別係佢地成日分唔到顏色亂填一通，玩具至少可以比佢地認到邊隻色打邊隻色吧~<br />\n<br />\n之前係fb見到黎緊有個活動都係用木玩具教小朋友認顏色呢...<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=923094871389227&amp;id=262869914078396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D923094871389227%26id%3D262869914078396&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=dd2fbd84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=923094871389227&amp;id=262869914078396</a>"}]}